Interface MdmQueryColumn

All Known Implementing Classes:
MdmAttribute, MdmBaseAttribute, MdmBaseMeasure, MdmColumn, MdmDerivedAttribute, MdmDerivedMeasure, MdmMeasure, MdmMultiValuedAttribute, MdmMultiValuedDerivedAttribute, MdmSingleValuedAttribute, MdmViewColumn
public interface MdmQueryColumn

An interface for an object that represents a column of a table or view that is associated with an MdmQuery.
